targets.rawSql:
WITH conversions as (
  SELECT
    date, campaign_name, sum(conversions) as "conversions"
  FROM google_cm_conversion_report
  WHERE 
    brand in($Brand) AND 
    product in($Product) AND 
    campaign_name in($Campaign) AND 
    activity in ($Activity)
  GROUP BY campaign_name, date),
cost AS (
  SELECT campaign_name, date, sum(cost) as "cost"
  FROM google_cm_campaign_report
  WHERE 
    $__timeFilter(date) AND
    brand in($Brand) AND 
    product in($Product) AND 
    campaign_name in($Campaign) AND 
    creative in($Creative)
    GROUP BY campaign_name, date)
SELECT 
  $__timeGroupAlias(conversions.date,$__interval),
  conversions / cost AS "cpa",
  conversions.campaign_name
FROM conversions LEFT JOIN cost 
ON conversions.campaign_name = cost.campaign_name AND conversions.date = cost.date
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(conversions.date)
GROUP BY 1, campaign_name
